          <div class="absolute -bottom-6 -right-6 w-full h-full bg-amber-100 rounded-lg -z-0"></div>
          <div class="absolute -top-6 -left-6 w-2/3 h-2/3 border-2 border-amber-500 rounded-lg -z-0"></div>
        </div>

        <!-- Company Description on Right -->
        <div class="order-1 lg:order-2">
          <span class="text-amber-500 text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.3em] mb-4 block">About Us</span>
          <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
            We are Septimius Properties
          </h2>
          <div class="w-24 h-1 bg-amber-500 mb-8"></div>
          
          <div class="space-y-6 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            <p class="text-lg">
              Septimius Properties is a Dublin-based company specialising in architecture, interiors and furniture, property management and premium rentals.
            </p>
            <p class="text-lg">
              Led by a qualified leadership team with extensive experience in delivering homes across Ireland, from inception and design to completion and ongoing management, we are dedicated to excellence in every stage of development.
            </p>
            <p class="text-lg">
              Combining professional expertise, innovative design, and a commitment to quality and sustainability, we create lasting value through bespoke projects and expertly managed properties.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Key Points -->
          <div class="mt-8 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
            <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-amber-500 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-700">Qualified Professionals</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-amber-500 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
